      Creates a problem generator with custom parameters
      Parameters:
      minSupply - Minimum supply in a source
      minDemand - Minimum demand in a destination
      maxSupply - Maximum supply in a source, may be overruled if needed
      maxDemand - Maximum demand in a destination, may be overruled if needed
      minSources - Minimum number of sources
      minDestinations - Minimum number of destinations
      maxSources - Maximum number of sources
      maxDestinations - Maximum number of destinations
